Package controller.filesManagers

Class FileManager

java.lang.Object
controller.filesManagers.FileManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileNames
public class FileManager extends Object implements FileNames
Class to load and save all kind of needed files (beside audios managed by AudioManager). Loaded images are stored statically in this class to be accesed without needing to reload them. Same for levels. Custom fonts are loaded in the environment.

  • Method Details

    • saveProfile

      public static void saveProfile(Profile p)
      Saves a profile in a text file named as the profile, with the following line strucure: *0 NAME *1 AVATAR *2 LEVEL *3 HEALTH *4 WIN GAMES *5 LOST GAMES *6 LAST SCORE *7 HIGH SCORE *8,9,10,11,12 SCORES
      Parameters:
      p - Profile to save NOTE : DO NOT MESS WITH FILES BECAUSE NO INTEGRITY CONTROLS ARE GIVEN

    • loadProfiles

      public static List<Profile> loadProfiles()
      Loads profiles from text files with the following structure. *0 NAME *1 AVATAR *2 LEVEL *3 HEALTH *4 WIN GAMES *5 LOST GAMES *6 LAST SCORE *7 HIGH SCORE *8,9,10,11,12 SCORES NOTE : DO NOT MESS WITH FILES BECAUSE NO INTEGRITY CONTROLS ARE GIVEN
